=== Origins ===
The shrine's founding is attributed to the [[:en:Hōji (era)|Hōji]] period (1247–1249).{{sfn|Adachi Historical Society|1978|p=231}} It is said that during the [[:en:Gosannen War|Later Three-Year War]], the Heian-period military commander [[:en:Minamoto no Yoshimitsu|Minamoto no Yoshimitsu]] prayed for victory at this location after witnessing an eagle. This marked the shrine’s establishment.{{sfn|Adachi Historical Society|1992|p=162}}

